Revision history for Text::CSV::Pivot

0.07  2018-06-16
      - Added key 'provides' to the Makefile.PL script.
      - Documented tool 'csv-pivot'.

0.06  2018-06-15
      - Added handy tool csv-pivot to play with it.

0.05  2018-06-14
      - Upgraded minimum perl version to v5.8.0 to get around the fail report.
        http://www.cpantesters.org/cpan/report/1fec5222-6efe-11e8-8fb1-ef5133556b3f

0.04  2018-06-13
      - Removed dependency on Moo as suggested by Steven Bray.

0.03  2018-03-06
      - Resolved issue RT #124606, thanks @james2vegas.

0.02  2018-03-05
      - Minor pod changes.

0.01  2018-02-27
      - First version released.